&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Would you like to support your local NHS Trust?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for Bank Staff to work in clinical and non-clinical roles in Solent NHS Trust&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you have any free time, want to earn some extra cash and support your Solent NHS Trust during this busy time then we want to hear from you.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for bank Nurses to cover a variety of areas within Portsmouth in a community ward setting. We have rehabilitation wards at St Marys Hospital Campus and Jubilee House in Portsmouth. We requrie nurses to cover a variety of shifts which they can to help out, but nights are not essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supportive Orientation Period&lt;/strong&gt;: Shadow shifts will be offered prior to working on our wards for training, development and to understand the working of the wards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information about this role please see the job description and to find out the hours and shifts patterns, please contact recruitment@solent.nhs.uk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note we are looking to hold interviews every week to support nurses in the current situation, therefore if shortlisted you will be called to interview before the closing date of this post.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re also recruiting for Nurses to work with in Southampton, you can view this vacancy under 449-BSS019 on NHS jobs. &lt;/p&gt;
